.consumption_summary
  .user_info
    #caff_daily.daily_info
      %span.big_num= current_user.daily_average_caffeine
      %p mgs caffeine per day
    .total_info
      %span.big_num= current_user.total_caffeine
      %p mgs caffeine total
  .tips
    %h3
      Caffeine (C
      %sub>8
      H
      %sub>10
      N
      %sub>4
      O
      %sub>2)
    %p Caffeine is a crystalline xanthine alkaloid and a stimulant drug. Caffeine is commonly consumed to decrease fatigue and increase alertness. Excess consumption can lead to caffeine addiction, increased blood pressure, sleep disruption.
    .advice
      %p
        %span.average_num 300 mgs per day is the American average.
      %p
        %span.average_num 600 mgs per day is the recommended maximum.